data.description: LOOKING FOR HORSE PROPERTY? This home has it all. This 10.27 acre property is all set up for you to just move right in and bring your horses. This equestrian property has a 3-stall barn with tac room, corral and dressage arena. Lots of trails and a beautiful seasonal pond. The home is amazing with vaulted ceilings in the living room and cozy fireplace, large open kitchen with a handy pantry, three good sized bedrooms, formal dining area and two full bathrooms. Nice porch in the front of the house and a additional room for in-laws or crafts. Large deck in the back of the house for gatherings. The garage is huge with a workshop area. Nice greenhouse and garden area for growing vegetables or flowers. There is an additional graded pad with a septic system in place for an additional ADU. This is a one-of-a-kind property that has it all. Horse properties are very hard to find. Look no further. COME TAKE A LOOK, YOU WON'T BE SORRY.
